rows.label: tlk70000029_03_msg0001
rows.name:
Looks like that blockhead Kaym is
actually starting to learn something
at last.

rows.label: tlk70000029_03_msg0002
rows.name: It's a load off my mind, I tell you.

rows.label: tlk70000029_03_msg0003
rows.name:
The truth is I'm not going to last
forever and the garden needs a skilled
pair of hands to manage it.

rows.label: tlk70000029_03_msg0004
rows.name:
I've definitely said some harsh words
along the way, but it was all worth it
for the sake of this garden...and my son.

rows.label: tlk70000029_03_msg0005
rows.name:
I could never say any of this to him,
though.
